wifi-radar for Debian
---------------------

dhclient3 is default DHCP client on Ubuntu and Debian. There is menu 
entry in Gnome under Applications, Internet for easier access to program. 
And, instead of sudo, this version uses gksudo, gtk frontend for sudo.

